For those looking for a bit of Taiwanese taste in Vegas, especially southern Taiwanese flavor (Tainan, Kaohsiung area), this is a great place to find it.
As the name suggests, the place isn't about big and fancy.
It is more about home cooking or comfort food, Taiwanese comfort food, to be exact.
I really enjoyed it.
Too bad I was too full.
Otherwise the shaved ice looked pretty good.
Definitely something you won't find anywhere on The Stripe.
I will return again.
I highly recommend it.

