Awesome traditional Taiwanese delicacies!
The soft tofu dessert (豆花) is one of the best I've tasted, and I'm from L.A.
The pork intestine thin noodle soup is also great.
They marinated the intestine and that just shows they really do follow the tradition.
Highly recommended!

